title: IDCE by Time-Streamer - Update 1.rar
description:
Im seeding this little update (26 MB), since i've mistakenly uploaded ID Collectors Edition with an old version of the mod coming with Strife. You just need to download this, unzip it into IDCE folder and replace the files. Thats it!


The update will bring new alternative fire modes for all weapons (remember to bind those keys) plus solve some minor quirks. Have Fun
